function [data,licks,mini_bouts,bouts] = analysis_wrapper(basedir,date,animal,doplot)
savedir = [basedir '/' date '/' animal];
[data] = read_datafiles(basedir,date,animal);
for i=1:length(data)
    licks{i} = findLicks(data(i));
    ilis{i} = getILIs(licks{i});
    [f,xi] = ksdensity(ilis{i}(ilis{i},0:.001:ceil(max(ilis{i})));
    fitObject = fit(xi(xi < 1)',f(xi < 1)','gauss2');
    mini_bout_thresh = fitObject.b1 + 3*fitObject.c1;
    bout_thresh = fitObject.b2 + 3*fitObject.c2;
    [miniBouts, bigBouts] = getBouts(licks{i},mini_bout_thresh,bout_thresh);
    mini_bouts{i} = miniBouts;
    bouts{i} = bigBouts;
end
end

